p <- list()
for (n in 1:length(outcomeslist)) {
    mname1 <- outcomeslist[[n]]
    m <- mRE[[paste0(mname1, "_RobVar")]]
    I2 <- i2_ml(m)

    if (n <= 8) {
        scalerange <- c(-30, 25)
    } else {
        scalerange <- c(-11, 13)
    }

    p[[n]] <- orchard_plot(m, mod = "1", xlab = "Effect size", group = "Study", k = TRUE,
        g = TRUE, transfm = "none", angle = 0, legend.pos = "top.out") + annotate(geom = "text",
        x = 0.6, y = 5, label = paste0("italic(I)^{2} == ", round(I2[1], 1), "*\"%\""),
        color = "black", parse = TRUE, size = 3) + scale_x_discrete(labels = c(outcomeslist[[n]])) +
        scale_fill_manual(values = colormap[[n]]) + scale_colour_manual(values = colormap[[n]]) +
        scale_size_continuous(range = c(1, 7), limits = c(0.1, 8), labels = scales::number_format(accuracy = 0.1)) +
        scale_y_continuous(limits = scalerange) + theme(legend.position = "right",
        axis.title.x = element_blank())
}

layout <- " A
            B
            C
            D
            E
            F
            G
            H
             "
Reduce("+", p[1:8]) + plot_layout(design = layout)

Reduce("+", p[9:length(outcomeslist)]) + plot_layout(design = layout)
